fields.name: How to verify your identity with this server
fields.value: To get more specific help, send me a message with the following format: `verify "UW TRON '26" "role"`

fields.name: How to verify your identity to become tron '26
fields.value: Send a message with the following format: `verify "UW TRON '26" "tron '26" "first_name last_name"` and a screenshot of your Quest screen with your full name visible attached to the message. An example of this process be found below.
